### 5.2 世界书卡片包

```dart
class LorebookCardPackage extends RFWPackage {
  LorebookCardPackage()
      : super(
          name: 'LorebookCard',
          version: '1.0.0',
          type: 'lorebookCard',
          schema: {
            'title': 'string',
            'content': 'string',
            'tags': 'array?',
